ception)) {\n                return DefinedClassResult.unsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading();\n            }\n            throw exception;\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static byte[] generatedClassBytes(String className) throws IOException {\n        String internalName = className.replace('.', '/');\n        ByteArrayOutputStream bytes = new ByteArrayOutputStream();\n        DataOutputStream output = new DataOutputStream(bytes);\n        output.writeInt(0xCAFEBABE);\n        output.writeShort(0);\n        output.writeShort(52);\n        output.writeShort(10);\n        output.writeByte(10);\n        output.writeShort(2);\n        output.writeShort(3);\n        output.writeByte(7);\n        output.writeShort(4);\n        output.writeByte(12);\n        output.writeShort(5);\n        output.writeShort(6);\n        output.writeByte(1);\n        output.writeUTF(\"java/lang/Object\");\n        output.writeByte(1);\n        output.writeUTF(\"<init>\");\n        output.writeByte(1);\n        output.writeUTF(\"()V\");\n        output.writeByte(7);\n        output.writeShort(8);\n        output.writeByte(1);\n        output.writeUTF(internalName);\n        output.writeByte(1);\n        output.writeUTF(\"Code\");\n        output.writeShort(0x0021);\n        output.writeShort(7);\n        output.writeShort(2);\n        output.writeShort(0);\n        output.writeShort(0);\n        output.writeShort(1);\n        output.writeShort(0x0001);\n        output.writeShort(5);\n        output.writeShort(6);\n        output.writeShort(1);\n        output.writeShort(9);\n        output.writeInt(17);\n        output.writeShort(1);\n        output.writeShort(1);\n        output.writeInt(5);\n        output.writeByte(0x2A);\n        output.writeByte(0xB7);\n        output.writeShort(1);\n        output.writeByte(0xB1);\n        output.writeShort(0);\n        output.writeShort(0);\n        output.writeShort(0);\n        output.flush();\n        return bytes.toByteArray();\n    }\n\n    private static void rethrowIfNotNativeImageDynamicClassLoadingError(Error error) {\n        if (!NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {\n            throw error;\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static boolean hasUnsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoadingError(Throwable throwable) {\n        Throwable current = throwable;\n        while (current != null) {\n            if (current instanceof Error error && NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {\n                return true;\n            }\n            current = current.getCause();\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n\n    private static final class FieldPatch {\n        private final Field field;\n        private final Object originalValue;\n\n        private FieldPatch(Field field, Object originalValue) {\n            this.field = field;\n            this.originalValue = originalValue;\n        }\n\n        private static FieldPatch save(String fieldName) throws ReflectiveOperationException {\n            Field field = ReflectUtils.class.getDeclaredField(fieldName);\n            field.setAccessible(true);\n            return new FieldPatch(field, field.get(null));\n        }\n\n        private void set(Object value) throws IllegalAccessException {\n            field.set(null, value);\n        }\n\n        private void restore() throws IllegalAccessException {\n            set(originalValue);\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static final class UnsafeDefineClassBridge {\n        public static Method defineClassMethod() throws NoSuchMethodException {\n            return UnsafeDefineClassBridge.class.getMethod(\n                    \"defineClass\",\n                    String.class,\n                    byte[].class,\n                    Integer.TYPE,\n                    Integer.TYPE,\n                    ClassLoader.class,\n                    ProtectionDomain.class\n            );\n        }\n\n        public static Class<?> defineClass(\n                String className,\n                byte[] bytecode,\n                int offset,\n                int length,\n                ClassLoader loader,\n                ProtectionDomain protectionDomain\n        ) {\n            return ((DefiningClassLoader) loader).define(className, bytecode, offset, length, protectionDomain);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class DefinedClassResult {\n        private final Class<?> definedClass;\n        private final boolean unsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading;\n\n        private DefinedClassResult(Class<?> definedClass, boolean unsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading) {\n            this.definedClass = definedClass;\n            this.unsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading = unsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading;\n        }\n\n        private static DefinedClassResult defined(Class<?> definedClass) {\n            return new DefinedClassResult(definedClass, false);\n        }\n\n        private static DefinedClassResult unsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading() {\n            return new DefinedClassResult(null, true);\n        }\n\n        private Class<?> definedClass() {\n            return definedClass;\n        }\n\n        private boolean isUnsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading() {\n            return unsupportedNativeImageDynamicClassLoading;\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static final class ConstructorTarget {\n        private final String message;\n\n        public ConstructorTarget(String message) {\n            this.message = message;\n        }\n\n        public String message() {\n            return message;\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static class ParentMethodContainer {\n        public String inheritedMessage(String value) {\n            return \"parent \" + value;\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static final class ChildMethodContainer extends ParentMethodContainer {\n        public String localMessage() {\n            return \"child\";\n        }\n    }\n\n    public interface SingleOperation {\n        String apply(String value);\n    }\n\n    private static final class DefiningClassLoader extends ClassLoader {\n        private DefiningClassLoader(ClassLoader parent) {\n            super(parent);\n        }\n\n        private Class<?> define(\n                String className,\n                byte[] bytecode,\n                int offset,\n                int length,\n                ProtectionDomain protectionDomain\n        ) {\n            return defineClass(className, bytecode, offset, length, protectionDomain);\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777770868939}}
